
# ice melts in nether
on place of ice, packed ice, or blue ice:
    environment of event-world is nether
    set event-block to air
    play sound "minecraft:block.fire.extinguish" with volume 0.5 with pitch (2.6 + (random number between -0.8 and 0.8)) at event-block
    draw (8 large smoke particle with particle speed 0 with distribution vector(0.25,0.25,0.25)) at event-block
